videos.description: During halftime of the Duke vs. South Carolina game, fans throw teddy bears onto the court that will be donated to the Prisma Health Children's Hospital and the Ronald McDonald House in Columbia.
videos.headline: South Carolina fans throw teddy bears onto court for charity
